ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of RICHARD JACKSON of Victoria, British Columbia, to be a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; and designation of RICHARD JACKSON to be Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Refugee Protection Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Vancouver Regional Office); effective May 11, 2003.
